title: HABIBIZ
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small and cozy restaurant run by two brothers. Serves fresh Oriental food, of which some is vegan, including made-in-house falafels, in addition to most of the sauces and all of the side dishes, like the tabbouleh salad or hummus. You can have your meal with rice or fresh made fries.
